England-Sri Lanka First Cricket Test Is Delayed by Rain at Cardiff

-- B y   P e t e r - J o s e p h   H e g a r t y
-- 
2011-05-26T10:46:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-26/england-sri-lanka-first-cricket-test-is-delayed-by-rain-at-cardiff.html
Rain has delayed the start of the
first cricket Test between  England  and  Sri Lanka  at Cardiff.  Play was due to begin at 11 a.m. There will now be an early
lunch at noon.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter-Joseph Hegarty at 
 phegarty@bloomberg.net  